node.text:
MY DAILY RITUAL WHEN I WAS DOWN BAD, THAT KEPT ME MOTIVATED/FOCUSED ON THE GOAL.
-
1. GRATITUTE 
-
FIND THE THINGS YOU ARE MOST GRATEFUL FOR, VISUALIZE AND FEEL THEM. & NO BS LIKE U HAVE NOTHING, IF UR BREATHING, U MOST DEF DO. GET GRATEFUL. 
-
BEING IN A GRATEFUL STATE, EMPOWERS YOUR MANIFESTATION TO A WHOLE NEW LEVEL & ALLOWS THE UNIVERSAL LAWS TO HEAR/ LISTEN TO YOU.
-
WENT I DIDNT HAVE MUCH, I WAS GRATEFUL FOR MY ABILITY TO DREAM & CHASE IT. BC EVERYDAY I WATCHED MY MENTALLY DISABLED BROTHER, NOT EVER ABLE TO DO THAT. 
-
2. VISUALIZATION
-
NOW THAT YOUR IN A GRATEFUL STATE, MANIFEST THE BIG VISION GOD GAVE YOU.
-
& DONT THINK ABT CARS/WATCHES/HOUSES. THAT STUFF IS IRRELEVANT.
-
VISUALIZE, THE MAN/WOMAN U ARE GOING TO BECOME. VISUALIZE URSELF @ SPEAKING ENGAGEMENTS, GIVING TO THE POOR, LEADING 1000s, MANAGING A BIG COMPANY.
-
BC AT THE END OF THE DAY. GOD & SOCIETY DONT CARE ABT THE THINGS U ACQUIRE, BUT THE PERSON U BECOME THAT BENEFITS SOCIETY. 
-
3. PRAYER
-
RESTORE YOUR FAITH & CONFIDENCE W GOD.
-
BC MY DAYS WERE ROUGH. FULL OF NEGATIVITY, DOUBT & FAILURES.
-
& THE ONLY WAY I WOULD GET THRU THEM, IS KNOWING THERES A BIGGER GOD GUIDING ME THRU IT ALL.
-
GO BE BLESSED TODAY
